# Schedule & Calendar

- Style through CSS in `web/src/styles/base.css` and schedule components in `web/src/components/ui/schedule/common/`.
- Hour-band zebra rows, visible grid lines, column dividers — no checkerboard day columns.
- Full-bleed planner; compose via `ScheduleViews.tsx` and `CalendarPageContent.tsx`.

Load `.cursor/skills/project/schedule/SKILL.md` before changing planner or month grid behavior.
